== About me

I'm currently working at [http://msi.sicnu.edu.cn/ School of Mathematical Science], [http://english.sicnu.edu.cn/EnglishIndex/webindex Sichuan Normal University] as a Lecturer. 
In 2020, I got my Ph.D. in Operational Research and Cybernetics
