I received my M.S. in Operational Research and Cybernetics under the supervision of [http://139.155.71.72:81/HomePage.aspx?ID=14 Prof. Fuquan Xia] in 2016 and B.S. in 
Mathematics and Applied Mathematic in 2013, both from Sichuan Normal University. [https://scholar.google.com/citations?user=7IbzkWIAAAAJ&hl=zh-CN&oi=sra Here] is my google scholar.


== Research Interests 
My research focuses on designing  efficient methods and developing the corresponding theory analysis for convex/nonconvex optimization problems with special structures, which
have wide applications in data analytics, image processing, machine learning, and uncertainty optimization, among others.
I am particularly interested in the following topics.
-  Variational inequality problem, Difference-of-convex problem and (Distributionally) Robust Optimization,  etc.


